.claude/

# Trademark: the Snapshot PB logo artwork is not distributed (see LICENSE / NOTICE).
# grip.scad's logo_file defaults to the committed logo.placeholder.svg (empty), so clones
# render unbranded with a clean console; the real art below is only used via a -D override.
Eblade/grip/openscad/logo.svg
# grip.stl embeds the engraved logo geometry, so it is not distributed either.
# Generate it locally from grip.scad (needs BOSL2; logo.svg present for a branded print).
Eblade/grip/stl/grip.stl
# grip.render.log is the console log from that render — a build artifact, not distributed.
Eblade/grip/stl/grip.render.log
